Package cs505.group1.state Description

This package provides developer tools to code a Finite State Machine using a a GrovePi button sensor. The button sensor can be used to change the state of the machine and/or to execute functions which change with the current state of the machine. Functionality is provided to set the state of the machine by method call as well.
